Bruce Wayne is Batman's real name. This masked vigilante is a familiar sight in the streets of Gotham City, where he protects the innocent and brings justice to the criminals who prey on them. Despite his lack of powers, Bruce Wayne is a formidable foe thanks to his mastery of martial arts and advanced technology. He is determined to eradicate crime and corruption in Gotham City, and he will not rest until his mission is accomplished. He is a highly motivated and dedicated hero, and his example has inspired many others to follow in his footsteps and use their own skills and abilities to fight evil and promote justice.